I have added 'python3-xmlschema ' as shown and failure message
changed to:

error: Command '['/usr/bin/python3.9', '-m', 'pip',
'--disable-pip-version-check', 'wheel', '--no-deps', '-w',
'/tmp/tmp3c4ogdyz', '--quiet', 'pbtestdata']' returned non-zero exit
